(321, 'Leap', 0, 0, 'Kha\'Zix leaps to an area, dealing physical damage upon landing. If he chooses to <font color=\'#00DD33\'>Evolve Wings</font>, Leap\'s range increases by 200 and the cooldown resets on champion kill or assist.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KhazixE.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:50;i:1;i:50;i:2;i:50;i:3;i:50;i:4;i:50;}', 'Mana', 'a:5:{i:0;i:20;i:1;i:18;i:2;i:16;i:3;i:14;i:4;i:12;}', 268, 'KhazixE', 0, 0, 0),
(322, 'Void Assault', 0, 0, 'Each rank allows Kha\'Zix to evolve one of his abilities, giving it a unique additional effect. When activated, Kha\'Zix becomes <font color=\'#91d7ee\'>Invisible</font>, triggering Unseen Threat and increasing Move Speed. If he chooses to <font color=\'#00DD33\'>Evolve Adaptive Cloaking</font>, Void Assault gains increased <font color=\'#91d7ee\'>Invisibility</font> duration, and an additional use.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KhazixR.png', 'a:3:{i:0;i:100;i:1;i:100;i:2;i:100;}', 'Mana', 'a:3:{i:0;i:100;i:1;i:85;i:2;i:70;}', 268, 'KhazixR', 0, 0, 0),
(323, 'Mark of the Kindred', 0, 0, 'Kindred can mark targets to Hunt. Successfully completing a Hunt permanently empowers Kindred\'s basic abilities. Every 4 hunts completed also increases Kindred\'s basic attack range.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/passive/Kindred_Passive.png', 'a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";}', 'Champion\'s passive', 'a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";}', 269, 'passive', 0, 0, 1),
(324, 'Dance of Arrows', 1, 0, 'Kindred tumbles and shoots up to three arrows at nearby targets.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KindredQ.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:35;i:1;i:35;i:2;i:35;i:3;i:35;i:4;i:35;}', 'Mana', 'a:5:{i:0;i:8;i:1;i:8;i:2;i:8;i:3;i:8;i:4;i:8;}', 269, 'KindredQ', 0, 0, 0),
(325, 'Wolf\'s Frenzy', 1, 0, 'Wolf enrages and attacks enemies around him.  Lamb passively gains stacks by moving and attacking. When fully charged, Lamb\'s next attack restores health.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KindredW.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:40;i:1;i:40;i:2;i:40;i:3;i:40;i:4;i:40;}', 'Mana', 'a:5:{i:0;i:18;i:1;i:17;i:2;i:16;i:3;i:15;i:4;i:14;}', 269, 'KindredW', 0, 0, 0),
(326, 'Mounting Dread', 1, 0, 'Lamb fires a carefully placed shot, slowing the target. If Lamb attacks the target two more times, her third attack instead directs Wolf to pounce on the enemy, savaging them for massive damage.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KindredEWrapper.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:0;i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:4;i:0;}', 'Mana', 'a:5:{i:0;i:14;i:1;i:13;i:2;i:12;i:3;i:11;i:4;i:10;}', 269, 'KindredEWrapper', 0, 0, 0),
(327, 'Lamb\'s Respite', 1, 0, 'Lamb grants all living things inside a zone a respite from death. Until the effect ends, nothing can die. At the end, units are healed.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KindredR.png', 'a:3:{i:0;i:100;i:1;i:100;i:2;i:100;}', 'Mana', 'a:3:{i:0;i:180;i:1;i:150;i:2;i:120;}', 269, 'KindredR', 0, 0, 0),
(328, 'Skaarl, the Cowardly Lizard', 0, 0, 'Kled rides his trusty steed, Skaarl, who takes damage for him. When Skaarl\'s health depletes, Kled dismounts.<br><br>While dismounted, Kled\'s abilities change and he deals less damage to champions. Kled can restore Skaarl\'s courage by fighting enemies. At maximum courage, Kled remounts with a portion of Skaarl\'s health.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/passive/Kled_P.png', 'a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";}', 'Champion\'s passive', 'a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";}', 270, 'passive', 0, 0, 1),
(329, 'Bear Trap on a Rope', 0, 0, 'Kled throws a bear trap that damages and hooks an enemy champion. If shackled for a short duration, the target takes additional physical damage and is yanked toward Kled.<br><br>When dismounted, this ability is replaced by Pocket Pistol, a ranged gun blast that knocks back Kled and restores courage.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KledQ.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:0;i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:4;i:0;}', 'empty', 'a:5:{i:0;i:11;i:1;i:10;i:2;i:9;i:3;i:8;i:4;i:7;}', 270, 'KledQ', 1, 0, 0),
(330, 'Violent Tendencies', 0, 0, 'Kled gains massive attack speed for four attacks. The fourth attack deals more damage.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/KledW.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:0;i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:4;i:0;}', 'empty', 'a:5:{i:0;i:12;i:1;d:10.5;i:2;i:9;i:3;d:7.5;i:4;i:6;}', 270, 'KledW', 0, 0, 0),
