(591, 'Roar of the Slayer', 1, 0, 'Sion fires a short range shockwave that damages and slows and reduces the Armor of the first enemy hit. If the shockwave hits a minion or monster, it will be knocked back, damaging, slowing, and reducing the Armor of all enemies that it passes through.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/SionE.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:35;i:1;i:40;i:2;i:45;i:3;i:50;i:4;i:55;}', 'Mana', 'a:5:{i:0;i:12;i:1;i:11;i:2;i:10;i:3;i:9;i:4;i:8;}', 322, 'SionE', 0, 0, 0),
(592, 'Unstoppable Onslaught', 1, 0, 'Sion charges in a direction, ramping up speed over time. He can steer his charge slightly with the mouse cursor location. When he collides with an enemy he deals damage and knocks them up based on the distance he has charged.', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/SionR.png', 'a:3:{i:0;i:100;i:1;i:100;i:2;i:100;}', 'Mana', 'a:3:{i:0;i:140;i:1;i:100;i:2;i:60;}', 322, 'SionR', 0, 0, 0),
