(830, 'Twilight Shroud', 1, 0, 'Akali drops a cover of smoke and briefly gains Move Speed. While inside the shroud, Akali becomes invisible and unable to be selected by enemy spells and attacks. Attacking or using abilities will briefly reveal her.  ', 'https://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/12.11.1/img/spell/AkaliW.png', 'a:5:{i:0;i:0;i:1;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:4;i:0;}', 'empty', 'a:5:{i:0;i:20;i:1;i:20;i:2;i:20;i:3;i:20;i:4;i:20;}', 370, 'AkaliW', 0, 0, 0),
